                },
                {
                    "start": 1796,
                    "end": 1798,
                    "mention": "10",
                    "ref_id": "BIBREF1"
                }
            ],
            "section": "",
            "ref_spans": []
        },
        {
            "text": "In conclusion, the clinical course of patients harboring the 2019-nCoV infection remains to be fully elucidated. We would suggest that health professionals investigate cardiac function as part of the routine care, and the data may shed light on whether myocardial damage is an independent predictor of adverse outcomes.",
